A young man in a worn leather motorcycle jacket sits cross-legged in meditation pose atop a vintage motorcycle parked on an empty coastal cliff road at golden hour. His eyes are closed but his shadow stretches behind him transformed into a roaring, wild beast made of swirling dark smoke and flame. The contrast between his serene posture and the fierce shadow creature creates tension. Warm orange sunset light bathes the scene while the shadow-beast burns with deep reds and blacks. Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures, detailed wind-blown grass, and that signature dreamy atmospheric haze. The ocean stretches to the horizon, waves rendered in gentle brushstrokes.
